channel.title: Please read. Unable to open output stream to character.log
channel.description: Hi. Maybe you've seen my last post that I didn't really get any help out of at all. I know i've set up my ports, classpaths/paths, and everything else correctly; but one thing is stopping me from making any progress on developing my server. Any time I try to edit code the output stream is unable to be accessed and any changes i have made to text files, ie character files is undone. would someone enlighten me as to how I can solve this problem once and for all? Thank you. -Flipzro[br][br][size=1]Posted on: February 08, 2009, 09:33:37 pm[/size][hr]: (
